####################################################
High Performance Conjugate Gradient Benchmark (HPCG)
####################################################

version 3.0
Checked in by David S. Scott

to create an executable, do

make arch=Linux_MPI

in this directory.

This will create an MPI executable "xhpcg" in the bin directory

Execute it with mpirun -np XX ./xhpcg

This will run with the parameters from the hpcg.dat file in bin


HPCG benchmark input file
Sandia National Laboratories; University of Tennessee, Knoxville
104 104 104
60


That is currently set to a local brick size of 104x104x104

It should produce two output files, .txt and .yaml


